 class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/4-meo-viet-so-yeu-ly-lich-cho-mot-cong-viec-ky-thuat-cap-dau-vao.html\/#Ky_nang_mem_Bao_gom\" title=\"K\u1ef9 n\u0103ng m\u1ec1m Bao g\u1ed3m:\">K\u1ef9 n\u0103ng m\u1ec1m Bao g\u1ed3m:<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/4-meo-viet-so-yeu-ly-lich-cho-mot-cong-viec-ky-thuat-cap-dau-vao.html\/#Ky_nang_cung_Bao_gom\" title=\"K\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u1ee9ng Bao g\u1ed3m:\">K\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u1ee9ng Bao g\u1ed3m:<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/4-meo-viet-so-yeu-ly-lich-cho-mot-cong-viec-ky-thuat-cap-dau-vao.html\/#3_Doi_sanh_So_yeu_ly_lich_cua_Ban_voi_Mo_ta_Cong_viec\" title=\"3. \u0110\u1ed1i s\u00e1nh S\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a B\u1ea1n v\u1edbi M\u00f4 t\u1ea3 C\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c\">3. \u0110\u1ed1i s\u00e1nh S\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a B\u1ea1n v\u1edbi M\u00f4 t\u1ea3 C\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/4-meo-viet-so-yeu-ly-lich-cho-mot-cong-viec-ky-thuat-cap-dau-vao.html\/#4_Lam_noi_bat_thanh_tich_cua_ban\" title=\"4. L\u00e0m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n\">4. L\u00e0m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-1'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/4-meo-viet-so-yeu-ly-lich-cho-mot-cong-viec-ky-thuat-cap-dau-vao.html\/#Achaumedia_cung_cap_dich_vu_thiet_ke_ho_so_nang_luc_o_dau_tai_Viet_nam\" title=\"Achaumedia cung c\u1ea5p d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t nam?\">Achaumedia cung c\u1ea5p d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t nam?<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7? \u0110\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00f4i khi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c.\u00a0Nh\u01b0ng ngay c\u1ea3 khi b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m, bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch vi\u1ebft m\u1ed9t s\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o c\u1eeda.<\/p>\n<p>H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng Achaumedia trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft th\u00eam 4 m\u1eb9o v\u1ec1 vi\u1ebft s\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Lam_theo_4_meo_viet_so_yeu_ly_lich_sau_de_giup_ban_the_hien_cac_ky_nang_cua_minh\"><\/span>L\u00e0m theo 4 m\u1eb9o vi\u1ebft s\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch sau \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1_Bao_gom_cac_Phan_So_yeu_ly_lich_nay\"><\/span>1. Bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c Ph\u1ea7n S\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch n\u00e0y<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><strong>T\u00ean v\u00e0 Th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean h\u1ec7:<\/strong>\u00a0email v\u00e0 s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><strong>T\u00f3m t\u1eaft chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n ho\u1eb7c &#8220;Gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 t\u00f4i&#8221; (T\u00f9y ch\u1ecdn):<\/strong>\u00a0m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 ni\u1ec1m \u0111am m\u00ea c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c n\u00e0y c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u00f3 li\u00ean quan c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><strong>Kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c:<\/strong>\u00a0li\u1ec7t k\u00ea b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 li\u00ean quan n\u00e0oc\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n th\u1eddi gian, to\u00e0n th\u1eddi gian, c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c t\u1ef1 do ho\u1eb7c t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi;\u00a0th\u1ef1c t\u1eadp;\u00a0h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c x\u00e3;\u00a0v\u00e0 c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u00ecnh nguy\u1ec7n<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><strong>K\u1ef9 n\u0103ng:<\/strong>\u00a0bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 li\u00ean quan ho\u1eb7c h\u1eefu \u00edch cho n\u01a1i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c nh\u01b0 k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng CNTT c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh th\u1ea1o v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh m\u00e1y t\u00ednh v\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><strong>H\u1ecdc v\u1ea5n:<\/strong>\u00a0b\u1eb1ng c\u1ea5p, ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1c m\u00f4n h\u1ecdc li\u00ean quan<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div class=\"prose lg:prose-xl\">\n<div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tiep_tuc_mau\"><\/span>Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1eabu<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"flex flex-wrap -mt-6\">\n<div class=\"w-full lg:w-12\/12 px-2\">\n<div class=\"ProseMirror byteContent prose lg:prose-xl\">\n<p dir=\"auto\">H\u00e3y nh\u1edb \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng t\u1eebng ph\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 theo c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd tuy\u1ec3n d\u1ee5ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ecdc.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1eabu s\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch m\u1eabu<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15088\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15088\" style=\"width: 500px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15088 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/images_800_r8dq4rs6vi.png\" alt=\"Mau-thiet-ke-CV\" width=\"500\" height=\"646\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/images_800_r8dq4rs6vi.png 500w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/images_800_r8dq4rs6vi-232x300.png 232w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15088\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">M\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2_Lam_noi_bat_cac_ky_nang_co_the_chuyen_giao_cua_ban\"><\/span>2. L\u00e0m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u00e1c k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n giao c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p dir=\"auto\">C\u00e1c <strong>k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n giao <\/strong>c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cho nh\u00e0 tuy\u1ec3n d\u1ee5ng th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb.<\/p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">K\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n giao l\u00e0 k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng\u00a0<strong>m\u1ec1m<\/strong>\u00a0ho\u1eb7c\u00a0\u00a0<strong>k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u1ee9ng<\/strong>\u00a0\u00a0c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n giao t\u1eeb ngh\u1ec1 nghi\u1ec7p n\u00e0y sang ngh\u1ec1 nghi\u1ec7p kh\u00e1c\u00a0<span class=\"attribution\" data-v-1727acc2=\"\"><span data-v-1727acc2=\"\">.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ky_nang_mem_Bao_gom\"><\/span>K\u1ef9 n\u0103ng m\u1ec1m Bao g\u1ed3m:<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p dir=\"auto\">L\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c theo nh\u00f3m<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ky_nang_cung_Bao_gom\"><\/span>K\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u1ee9ng Bao g\u1ed3m:<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Kinh nghi\u1ec7m s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m nh\u01b0 Powerpoint v\u00e0 Photoshop<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p dir=\"auto\">K\u1ef9 n\u0103ng l\u1eadp tr\u00ecnh m\u00e1y t\u00ednh<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div class=\"prose lg:prose-xl\">\n<div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3_Doi_sanh_So_yeu_ly_lich_cua_Ban_voi_Mo_ta_Cong_viec\"><\/span>3. \u0110\u1ed1i s\u00e1nh S\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a B\u1ea1n v\u1edbi M\u00f4 t\u1ea3 C\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"flex flex-wrap -mt-6\">\n<div class=\"w-full lg:w-12\/12 px-2\">\n<div class=\"ProseMirror byteContent prose lg:prose-xl\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><strong>\u0110i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh s\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/strong> cho ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p dir=\"auto\">\u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o\u00a0<strong>l\u00e0m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u00e1ch b\u1ea1n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>L\u00e0m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u00e1c k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/strong> li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00f3. Ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u00e0nh th\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u1edbi:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>C\u00e1c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh m\u00e1y t\u00ednh<\/li>\n<li>Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m \/ n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng<\/li>\n<li>C\u01a1 s\u1edf d\u1eef li\u1ec7u<\/li>\n<li>Ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef m\u00e3 h\u00f3a<\/li>\n<li>C\u00f4ng c\u1ee5.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n cho m\u1ed7i.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"4_Lam_noi_bat_thanh_tich_cua_ban\"><\/span>4. L\u00e0m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><strong>Hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb, kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i!\u00a0<\/strong>C\u00e2n nh\u1eafc cung c\u1ea5p m\u1ed9t li\u00ean k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn danh m\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c m\u1eabu c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n trong s\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><strong>Bao g\u1ed3m nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh t\u1ef1u ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/strong>\u00a0.\u00a0B\u1ea1n l\u00e0 sinh vi\u00ean l\u1eadp tr\u00ecnh m\u00e1y t\u00ednh v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec3m trung b\u00ecnh 4.0?\u00a0Ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 l\u1ebd b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong cu\u1ed9c thi hackathon.\u00a0L\u00e0m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n!<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p dir=\"auto\">N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, h\u00e3y\u00a0<strong>\u0111\u1ecbnh l\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch<\/strong>\u00a0v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1eef li\u1ec7u v\u00e0 con s\u1ed1.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h1><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Achaumedia_cung_cap_dich_vu_thiet_ke_ho_so_nang_luc_o_dau_tai_Viet_nam\"><\/span>Achaumedia cung c\u1ea5p d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t nam?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h1>\n<p>S\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, Achaumedia cung c\u1ea5p d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c t\u1ea1i 63 t\u1ec9nh th\u00e0nh Vi\u1ec7t Nam bao g\u1ed3m: An Giang, B\u00e0 R\u1ecba-V\u0169ng T\u00e0u, B\u1ea1c Li\u00eau, B\u1eafc K\u1ea1n, B\u1eafc Giang,B\u1eafc Ninh, B\u1ebfn Tre, B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, B\u00ecnh \u0110\u1ecbnh, B\u00ecnh Ph\u01b0\u1edbc, B\u00ecnh Thu\u1eadn, C\u00e0 Mau, Cao B\u1eb1ng, C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 (TP),\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng (TP), \u0110\u1eafk L\u1eafk, \u0110\u1eafk N\u